commitResults.messageTitle: Implement an initial skeletal version of Duke
Restructure Greet class to static methods in the Duke class

commitResults.messageBody:
- Duke logo, decorative line, and paddings are changed to constants
- Echos user commands, and exits when the user types "bye"

- Add the ability to store whatever task entered by the user
- Display the list of tasks when requested

commitResults.messageTitle: Use a class to represent tasks
commitResults.messageBody:
A more natural approach to represent tasks with
class, as it enables encapsulation and separation
of concerns.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add the ability to mark tasks as done
